            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Marti <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Accius <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uirina</ex></expan> Se<lb break="no" n="3"/>cundus Eburo<lb break="no" n="4"/>duni <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>eneficiarius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Memmi <lb n="5"/>Clementis <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>item templum de suo <expan><abbr>reno</abbr><ex>vavit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Since the first part of the text is well realized, it is possible that the last line, where there are many ligatures, was added later.</p>
            </div>
